       <!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
  <title>Jazz Club & Coffee | Formation Barista 2026 – Lima</title>
  <!-- Fonts -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Raleway:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Special+Elite&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      background: #070503;
      color: #f5ead6;
      font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.5;
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    /* palette jazz */
    :root {
      --gold: #c9a84c;
      --gold-light: #e0bc6a;
      --cream: #f5ead6;
      --dark-bg: #070503;
      --dark-card: #0f0b08;
      --border-gold-light: rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.25);
      --shadow-gold: rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.2);
    }

    /* header fixe */
    header {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      z-index: 200;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 14px 48px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(7,5,3,0.96), transparent);
      backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
      pointer-events: auto;
    }

    .logo-img {
      height: 52px;
      width: auto;
      object-fit: contain;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 12px rgba(201,168,76,0.4));
    }

    nav a {
      color: var(--cream);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-left: 32px;
      opacity: 0.7;
      transition: 0.25s;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      opacity: 1;
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    /* BANNER JAZZ */
    .banner {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow: hidden;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-end;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .banner-img {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      filter: brightness(0.55) saturate(1.05);
    }

    .spots {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .spot1 {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 45%;
      height: 100%;
      background: conic-gradient(from 0deg at 50% 0%, transparent 0deg, rgba(255,220,130,0.0) 10deg, rgba(255,220,130,0.28) 16deg, rgba(255,210,100,0.16) 22deg, transparent 32deg);
      transform-origin: top center;
      animation: beam1 8s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.6, 1) infinite;
    }

    @keyframes beam1 {
      0% { left: -30%; opacity: 0; transform: rotate(-15deg); }
      6% { opacity: 1; }
      45% { left: 90%; opacity: 0.9; transform: rotate(10deg); }
      55% { left: 95%; opacity: 0; transform: rotate(12deg); }
      100% { left: 95%; opacity: 0; transform: rotate(12deg); }
    }

    .spot2 {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      right: 0;
      width: 40%;
      height: 100%;
      background: conic-gradient(from 0deg at 50% 0%, transparent 0deg, rgba(255,220,130,0.0) 10deg, rgba(255,200,80,0.24) 17deg, rgba(255,210,100,0.12) 24deg, transparent 34deg);
      transform-origin: top center;
      animation: beam2 8s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.6, 1) infinite;
      animation-delay: 4s;
    }

    @keyframes beam2 {
      0% { right: -30%; opacity: 0; transform: rotate(15deg); }
      6% { opacity: 1; }
      45% { right: 88%; opacity: 0.85; transform: rotate(-10deg); }
      55% { right: 93%; opacity: 0; transform: rotate(-12deg); }
      100% { right: 93%; opacity: 0; transform: rotate(-12deg); }
    }

    .ambient {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse 65% 55% at 42% 48%, rgba(201,168,76,0.09) 0%, transparent 72%);
      animation: ambientBreathe 5s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    @keyframes ambientBreathe {
      from { opacity: 0.35; }
      to { opacity: 1; }
    }

    .banner-vignette {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(7,5,3,0.42) 0%, transparent 32%, transparent 58%, rgba(7,5,3,0.88) 100%);
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .banner-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 10;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 0 24px 100px;
    }

    .banner-content h1 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6.5rem);
      color: var(--cream);
      text-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(201,168,76,0.6);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .tagline {
      font-size: clamp(0.7rem, 1.8vw, 1rem);
      letter-spacing: 0.44em;
      color: var(--gold);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-top: 14px;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .scroll-hint {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 26px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      font-size: 0.66rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.34em;
      color: var(--gold);
      z-index: 12;
      animation: nudge 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes nudge {
      0%,100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); opacity: 0.45; }
      50% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(9px); opacity: 1; }
    }

    /* winamp style - playlist jazz */
    .playlist-section {
      background: #0a0705;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border-gold-light);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-gold-light);
    }

    .playlist-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 8px 24px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #1c1106, #0d0a07);
    }

    .winamp-title {
      font-family: 'Special Elite', cursive;
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em;
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    .eq-bars {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2px;
      align-items: flex-end;
      height: 16px;
    }

    .eq-bar {
      width: 3px;
      background: var(--gold);
      border-radius: 1px;
      animation: eq 0.42s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    }

    .eq-bar:nth-child(1) { animation-duration: 0.38s; height: 60%; }
    .eq-bar:nth-child(2) { animation-duration: 0.52s; height: 90%; }
    .eq-bar:nth-child(3) { animation-duration: 0.44s; height: 40%; }
    .eq-bar:nth-child(4) { animation-duration: 0.6s; height: 75%; }
    .eq-bar:nth-child(5) { animation-duration: 0.35s; height: 55%; }

    @keyframes eq {
      from { transform: scaleY(0.25); }
      to { transform: scaleY(1); }
    }

    .track-display {
      background: #050302;
      border: 1px solid #2a1f0a;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      font-family: 'Special Elite', cursive;
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      color: #d4a843;
      flex: 1;
      white-space: nowrap;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .ticker-wrap {
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 8px 0;
      background: #080603;
    }

    .ticker-track {
      display: flex;
      width: max-content;
      animation: scroll 62s linear infinite;
    }

    .ticker-item {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 0 28px;
      font-family: 'Special Elite', cursive;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      color: var(--gold);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    @keyframes scroll {
      from { transform: translateX(0); }
      to { transform: translateX(-50%); }
    }

    /* SECTION FORMATION - STRUCTURE LISIBLE */
    .formation-section {
      max-width: 1400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 70px 48px 80px;
    }

    .section-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 56px;
    }

    .section-header .badge {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.4em;
      color: var(--gold);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      background: rgba(201,168,76,0.12);
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 6px 20px;
      border-radius: 40px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .section-header h2 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-top: 20px;
      color: var(--cream);
    }

    .section-header p {
      color: rgba(245,234,214,0.7);
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 16px auto 0;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* grille modules - amélioration lisibilité */
    .modules-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(360px, 1fr));
      gap: 32px;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .module-card {
      background: #0f0b08;
      border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.25);
      border-radius: 28px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      overflow: hidden;
      backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }

    .module-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(201,168,76,0.7);
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 35px -12px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
    }

    .module-header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(201,168,76,0.15), rgba(0,0,0,0.4));
      padding: 22px 26px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.25);
    }

    .module-num {
      font-family: 'Special Elite', cursive;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: var(--gold-light);
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .module-title {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.55rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-top: 10px;
      color: var(--cream);
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .module-list {
      padding: 22px 26px 28px;
    }

    .module-list ul {
      list-style: none;
    }

    .module-list li {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      padding-left: 24px;
      position: relative;
      color: rgba(245,234,214,0.85);
      line-height: 1.45;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    .module-list li::before {
      content: "♪";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      opacity: 0.8;
      top: 0;
    }

    /* pied de page formation */
    .formation-footer-badge {
      margin-top: 60px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
      padding-top: 40px;
    }

    .certif-tag {
      background: rgba(201,168,76,0.1);
      padding: 8px 24px;
      border-radius: 60px;
      display: inline-block;
      font-family: 'Special Elite', cursive;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    /* mini menu */
    .menu-mini {
      background: #0f0b08;
      padding: 14px 48px;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.1);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.1);
    }

    .menu-mini a {
      color: var(--gold);
      margin: 0 20px;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-decoration: none;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: 0.2s;
    }

    .menu-mini a:hover {
      color: var(--cream);
    }

    /* about section */
    .about-container {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 52px;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .about-text-block {
      flex: 1.3;
    }

    .about-info-block {
      flex: 0.8;
      background: #0f0b08;
      border-left: 2px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.4);
      padding-left: 36px;
    }

    .badge-inline {
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.35em;
      color: var(--gold);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      background: rgba(201,168,76,0.1);
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 4px 14px;
      border-radius: 30px;
    }

    .about-text-block h2 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin: 18px 0 20px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .about-text-block p {
      color: rgba(245,234,214,0.75);
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .features-list {
      display: flex;
      gap: 28px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    .feature-item {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    .info-hours {
      font-family: 'Special Elite', cursive;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }

    /* footer */
    .footer-site {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.12);
      padding: 32px 48px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 20px;
      background: #030201;
    }

    .footer-site p {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: rgba(245,234,214,0.35);
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }

    .footer-site a {
      color: rgba(201,168,76,0.7);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: 0.2s;
    }

    .footer-site a:hover {
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      header { padding: 12px 20px; }
      nav { display: none; }
      .formation-section { padding: 45px 20px; }
      .modules-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 24px; }
      .about-container { flex-direction: column; }
      .about-info-block { border-left: none; border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.3); padding-left: 0; padding-top: 28px; margin-top: 10px; }
      .menu-mini { padding: 12px 16px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; gap: 12px; }
      .menu-mini a { margin: 0 8px; }
      .footer-site { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; padding: 28px 20px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <img src="logo.png" alt="Jazz Club Coffee" class="logo-img" onerror="this.style.display='none';">
  <nav>
    <a href="#formation">Formation</a>
    <a href="#menu-lia">Menu</a>
    <a href="#about">À propos</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<!-- BANNER PRINCIPAL -->
<div class="banner">
  <img src="banner.png" alt="Jazz club ambiance" class="banner-img" onerror="this.src='https://placehold.co/1600x1000/1e1915/c9a84c?text=Jazz+Coffee+Lima+Barista'">
  <div class="ambient"></div>
  <div class="spots"><div class="spot1"></div><div class="spot2"></div></div>
  <div class="banner-vignette"></div>
  <div class="banner-content">
    <h1>Barista Pro 2026</h1>
    <p class="tagline">Formation complète — Take away concept</p>
    <div style="margin-top: 18px; font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 0.2rem; opacity:0.85;">Lima · Surco · Certification</div>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-hint">↓ 13 modules ↓</div>
</div>

<!-- PLAYLIST JAZZ -->
<div class="playlist-section">
  <div class="playlist-header">
    <div class="eq-bars"><div class="eq-bar"></div><div class="eq-bar"></div><div class="eq-bar"></div><div class="eq-bar"></div><div class="eq-bar"></div></div>
    <span class="winamp-title">JAZZ SESSIONS · BARISTA SPIRIT</span>
    <div class="track-display" id="nowPlaying">🎷 Blue in Green · Miles Davis</div>
  </div>
  <div class="ticker-wrap">
    <div class="ticker-track" id="ticker">
      <span class="ticker-item">♪ 01 · Autumn Leaves · Cannonball Adderley</span>
      <span class="ticker-item">♪ 02 · Take Five · Dave Brubeck</span>
      <span class="ticker-item">♪ 03 · So What · Miles Davis</span>
      <span class="ticker-item">♪ 04 · Round Midnight · Thelonious Monk</span>
      <span class="ticker-item">♪ 05 · St. Thomas · Sonny Rollins</span>
      <span class="ticker-item">♪ 06 · Song for my Father · Horace Silver</span>
      <span class="ticker-item">♪ 07 · Blue Train · John Coltrane</span>
      <span class="ticker-item">♪ 08 · Moanin' · Art Blakey</span>
      <span class="ticker-item">♪ 09 · All Blues · Miles Davis</span>
      <span class="ticker-item">♪ 10 · Body and Soul · Coleman Hawkins</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- SECTION FORMATION COMPLÈTE 13 MODULES -->
<div id="formation" class="formation-section">
  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="badge">Espresso · Mouture · Latte Art · Take away</div>
    <h2>Plan de formation Barista<br>Professionnel 2026</h2>
    <p>De la graine à la tasse, en passant par la gestion commerciale et l'organisation du coffee shop. Programme complet adapté à votre projet Lima — coffee shop take-away, matcha, armoise et infusions.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="modules-grid">
    <!-- MODULE 1 -->
    <div class="module-card"><div class="module-header"><div class="module-num">MODULE 01</div><div class="module-title">Le café – de la plante à la tasse</div></div><div class="module-list"><ul><li>1.1 – La plante et ses origines</li><li>1.2 – La récolte et les méthodes de traitement</li><li>1.3 – La torréfaction : types et impacts sur le goût</li><li>1.4 – La conservation et la fraîcheur des grains</li></ul></div></div>
    <!-- MODULE 2 -->
    <div class="module-card"><div class="module-header"><div class="module-num">MODULE 02</div><div class="module-title">La mouture</div></div><div class="module-list"><ul><li>2.1 – Les types de moulins (lames vs meules)</li><li>2.2 – Le réglage de la mouture pour espresso</li><li>2.3 – L'importance de la régularité granulométrique</li><li>2.4 – Ajuster la mouture selon humidité et âge du café</li></ul></div></div>
    <!-- MODULE 3 -->
    <div class="module-card"><div class="module-header"><div class="module-num">MODULE 03</div><div class="module-title">La machine espresso professionnelle</div></div><div class="module-list"><ul><li>3.1 – Types de machines (groupe, boiler, manuel/auto)</li><li>3.2 – Composants clés : groupe, buse vapeur, manomètres</li><li>3.3 – Mise en route et préchauffage</li><li>3.4 – Commandes et programmation</li></ul></div></div>
    <!-- MODULE 4 -->
    <div class="module-card"><div class="module-header"><div class="module-num">MODULE 04</div><div class="module-title">Portefiltre et tassage</div></div><div class="module-list"><ul><li>4.1 – Porte-filtres simple, double, filtre aveugle</li><li>4.2 – Dosage : poids de café moulu (grammage)</li><li>4.3 – Répartition du café dans le panier</li><li>4.4 – Tassage : pression, angle, gestuelle</li></ul></div></div>
    <!-- MODULE 5 -->
    <div class="module-card"><div class="module-header"><div class="module-num">MODULE 05</div><div class="module-title">L'extraction de l'espresso</div></div><div class="module-list"><ul><li>5.1 – Paramètres d'extraction : temps, température, pression</li><li>5.2 – Flow : lecture du débit et de la couleur</li><li>5.3 – Défauts : sous-extraction, sur-extraction</li><li>5.4 – Diagnostic par dégustation</li></ul></div></div>
    <!-- MODULE 6 -->
    <div class="module-card"><div class="module-header"><div class="module-num">MODULE 06</div><div class="module-title">Le lait et la mousse</div></div><div class="module-list"><ul><li>6.1 – Types de lait (vache, végétaux) comportements</li><li>6.2 – Buse vapeur : utilisation et purge</li><li>6.3 – Montée en température (contrôle manuel)</li><li>6.4 – Incorporation d'air pour micro-mousse onctueuse</li><li>6.5 – Nettoyage immédiat de la buse</li></ul></div></div>
    <!-- MODULE 7 -->
    <div class="module-card"><div class="module-header"><div class="module-num">MODULE 07</div><div class="module-title">Latte art</div></div><div class="module-list"><ul><li>7.1 – Bases du versage (free pouring)</li><li>7.2 – Le cœur (heart)</li><li>7.3 – La feuille (rosetta)</li><li>7.4 – La tulipe (tulip)</li><li>7.5 – Topping et drawing (stylets)</li></ul></div></div>
    <!-- MODULE 8 -->
    <div class="module-card"><div class="module-header"><div class="module-num">MODULE 08</div><div class="module-title">Boissons à base de café & signatures</div></div><div class="module-list"><ul><li>8.1 – Classiques : ristretto, espresso, lungo</li><li>8.2 – Lactées : cappuccino, latte, flat white, macchiato</li><li>8.3 – Sans café : matcha latte, thé, infusion, armoise</li><li>8.4 – Recettes signatures et créations personnalisées</li></ul></div></div>
    <!-- MODULE 9 -->
    <div class="module-card"><div class="module-header"><div class="module-num">MODULE 09</div><div class="module-title">Méthodes d'infusion douces</div></div><div class="module-list"><ul><li>9.1 – French press</li><li>9.2 – V60 (Hario) et Dripper</li><li>9.3 – Aeropress</li><li>9.4 – Chemex</li><li>9.5 – Cold brew (préparation en batch)</li></ul></div></div>
    <!-- MODULE 10 -->
    <div class="module-card"><div class="module-header"><div class="module-num">MODULE 10</div><div class="module-title">Organisation du poste de travail</div></div><div class="module-list"><ul><li>10.1 – Mise en place (mise en place)</li><li>10.2 – Gestion des flux et des commandes</li><li>10.3 – Optimisation du temps en take-away</li><li>10.4 – Service et relation client rapide</li></ul></div></div>
    <!-- MODULE 11 -->
    <div class="module-card"><div class="module-header"><div class="module-num">MODULE 11</div><div class="module-title">Maintenance et hygiène</div></div><div class="module-list"><ul><li>11.1 – Nettoyage journalier des groupes et porte-filtres</li><li>11.2 – Utilisation du filtre aveugle (backflush)</li><li>11.3 – Nettoyage du moulin</li><li>11.4 – Traitement de l'eau et détartrage</li><li>11.5 – Règles HACCP appliquées au café</li></ul></div></div>
    <!-- MODULE 12 -->
